!CPX Di85 He15
Diopside             -label default
Diopside             -label h+
Hedenbergite         -label default
Hedenbergite         -label h+ 

!plagioclase An7
Anorthite            -label default
Anorthite            -label h+
Anorthite            -label oh-
Albite               -label default
Albite               -label h+
Albite               -label oh-

! Secondary minerals
!amphibole
