Tremolite            -label h+

!serpentine
Chrysotile            -label default
Chrysotile            -label h+
Talc                  -label default
Talc                  -label h+

! Oxides
!Hematite             1.0E-10  ssa 5d-3

Quartz                -label h+
Quartz                -label oh-

! Mica
