POROSITY
porosity_update               false
END

INITIAL_CONDITIONS
Initial                     1-500 1-1  1-1
END

PRIMARY_SPECIES
H+
Al+++
O2(aq)
Mg++
Ca++
Fe++
Fe+++
HCO3-  
Cl-
K+
Na+
SO4--
SiO2(aq)
END
 
SECONDARY_SPECIES 
OH-
Al(OH)2+
AlO2-
AlOH++
CO3--
CO2(aq)
CaCl+
CaCl2(aq)
!CaOH+
CaSO4(aq)
FeCl+
FeCl2(aq)
!FeOH+
!FeSO4(aq)
!MgSO4(aq)
MgCO3(aq)
HSO4-
HSiO3-
KCl(aq)
!KOH(aq)
KSO4-
NaOH(aq)
!NaSO4-
END

GASES
